<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='977904' id='t-977904'>the could-do-better-next-times,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='980756' id='t-980756'>then we might never feel it.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='984055' id='t-984055'>A lot of people have asked me, what next?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='987631' id='t-987631'>Right now, I am very happy just recovering
